name: Glory of Commerce
description:
Portraying Mercury, the god of the merchants alongside Hercules and Minerva, the “Progress with Mental and Physical Force” or more known as “Glory of Commerce” sculptor captivates me, recently. The work means that for success to be achieved, it takes a mental and physical force.

 I think that represent what I am trying to say here. Through this celebration post, I would like to remind myself about the work that I did, to keep focus on building myself through every project ahead and find balance within my mind and body.

----------
This drop is for celebrating my 1000 friends in twitter and also marking my 1 month journey in this world.

Thank you for the support, WAGMI!
